<emphasis id="B29CEAB9FF85FE4AFE0CAF91FDC8F74F" box="[402,535,2205,2245]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="88">Biology.</emphasis>
As far as has been observed by the author, this species frequents the same haunts as do most of the species of 
<emphasis id="B29CEAB9FF85FE4AFBF7AFCAFADDF764" box="[1129,1282,2246,2286]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="88">
